text: Eadward kyngc gret Wulwi biscop & Gyrþ eorl & ealle mine þeignes on Oxenfordescire freondlice.

& ic kiþe eow þæt ic habbe gegifon Langtun Criste & Seinte Petre into <Westmunstre> mid saca & mid socne, mid tolle & mid teame & infangenan þeofe & <on> eallan þingan swa full & swa forð swa hit me silfan on hande stod.
& ic nelle geþafian þæt ænig man þær on ænig <onstingc> habbe buton se abbot & þæ gebroðra þær binnan.
